  "instructions": [
    "Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "Thread chicken pieces onto skewers, leaving a small space between each piece.",
    "In a small bowl, mix together olive oil, smoky paprika, brazilian-style seasoning, and garlic.",
    "Brush the mixture onto both sides of the chicken.",
    "Season with salt and pepper to taste.",
    "Grill skewers for 8-10 minutes, turning occasionally, until chicken is cooked through.",
